caption: Partial Enrollment Requests
created: 20260405120000000
modified: 20260405120000000
title: Policy6005(s3)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Due to practical difficulties and concerns regarding equitable treatment of students, the Board does not operate a hybrid home instruction/formal school program. Accordingly, the Board does not permit resident homeschooled students to enroll in the school district on a part-time basis.
